OL,3,C'Exceptional' tartan archive gifted to
OL,4,Cthe nation
OL,6,FAn "exceptional" archive of almost 800
OL,7,Fhistoric tartan samples has been
OL,8,Fgifted to the nation.
OL,10,FThe textiles, some more than 200 years
OL,11,Fold, were produced by J&D Paton, one
OL,12,Fof the largest tartan manufacturers of
OL,13,Fthe 19th and 20th centuries.
OL,15,FThe collection has now been donated to
OL,16,FNational Museums Scotland (NMS) by
OL,17,FStuart Paton, the great-great grandson
OL,18,Fof the firm's founder.
OL,26,@nD@DOUnD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779069821
OL,3,C'Exceptional' tartan archive gifted to
OL,4,Cthe nation
OL,6,FIt includes textiles created for Queen
OL,7,FVictoria and the royal family during
OL,8,Fthe 19th-century Highland revival,
OL,9,Fmilitary fabrics supplied to Scottish
OL,10,Fregiments, rare examples of tartans
OL,11,Fwoven for women's fashion and
OL,12,Fpreviously unrecorded clan tartans.
OL,14,FExperts said the collection, which
OL,15,Fspans the history of the firm from its
OL,16,Ffoundation in the 1820s to its closure
OL,17,Fin the 1960s, could potentially
OL,18,Frewrite the understanding of tartan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779069821
OL,3,C'Exceptional' tartan archive gifted to
OL,4,Cthe nation
OL,6,FIt will now be catalogued and made
OL,7,Favailable for research at the National
OL,8,FMuseums Collection Centre in Edinburgh.
OL,10,FDr Mhairi Maxwell, curator of modern &
OL,11,Fcontemporary history at NMS, said:
OL,12,F"Tartan is one of the most
OL,13,Frecognisable symbols of Scotland and
OL,14,Fthe exceptional J&D Paton collection
OL,15,Fis of immense importance to ongoing
OL,16,Fresearch into the history of the
OL,17,Ficonic textile.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779069821
OL,3,C'Exceptional' tartan archive gifted to
OL,4,Cthe nation
OL,6,F"We have only just begun to uncover
OL,7,Fthe stories woven through this
OL,8,Fremarkable archive and I've no doubt
OL,9,Fthere are many discoveries waiting to
OL,10,Fbe made, all thanks the generosity of
OL,11,FStuart Paton and his family."
OL,13,FJ&D Paton was at its most popular in
OL,14,Fthe late 19th century and carried on
OL,15,Fproduction through the two world wars.
OL,17,FAt its peak the firm, family run for
OL,18,Ffive generations, employed hundreds of
OL,19,Fpeople across four factory sites in
OL,20,FStirlingshire, near Tillicoultry.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779069821
OL,3,C'Exceptional' tartan archive gifted to
OL,4,Cthe nation
OL,6,FIt produced internationally-renowned
OL,7,Ftartans and tweeds, and won awards for
OL,8,Ffine fashion textiles which were
OL,9,Fsometimes woven through with silk.
OL,11,FPrevious knowledge of the history of
OL,12,Ftartan in the 18th, 19th and 20th
OL,13,Fcentury has been dominated by what is
OL,14,Fknown about Wilsons of Bannockburn,
OL,15,Fanother "prolific" producer of tartan
OL,16,Fbased in Stirlingshire.
OL,18,FDr Maxwell said the acquisition of the
OL,19,FJ&D Paton archive will help provide a
OL,20,Ffuller picture of tartan production
OL,21,Fduring that period.
OL,26,@wD@IOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779069821
OL,3,C'Exceptional' tartan archive gifted to
OL,4,Cthe nation
OL,6,FShe said: "We are really hoping that
OL,7,Fthis will rewrite the history of
OL,8,Ftartan production as we currently
OL,9,Funderstand it."
OL,11,FNMS said the archive provides a rare
OL,12,Fand detailed picture of the history of
OL,13,Fmass manufacturing at a time when
OL,14,Ftartans were expanding into global
OL,15,Fmarketplaces and new fashions.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779069821
OL,3,C'Exceptional' tartan archive gifted to
OL,4,Cthe nation
OL,6,FDr Maxwell said: "J&D Paton also seem
OL,7,Fto have been the pioneers of more
OL,8,Ffashionable tartans and that's really
OL,9,Fexciting, because the time that they
OL,10,Fwere really mass-producing these
OL,11,Ftartans is the peak of the kind of
OL,12,Fromanticism of Scotland.
OL,14,F"The idea that Queen Victoria was
OL,15,Fdecking out Balmoral in her tartans
OL,16,Fand was herself pictured in beautiful
OL,17,Ftartan shawls, it was no surprise then
OL,18,Fthat there would be a demand from the
OL,19,Fmiddle classes and the elite to also
OL,20,Fhave a bit of their own fashionable
OL,21,Ftartan.
OL,26,@nD@ROUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779069821
OL,3,C'Exceptional' tartan archive gifted to
OL,4,Cthe nation
OL,6,F"So, we're really hoping this archive
OL,7,Fcan shed light on that and we'll be
OL,8,Flooking at the colours that were
OL,9,Fpopular."
OL,11,FShe said the archive, featuring a
OL,12,F"kaleidoscope of tartan", has been
OL,13,F"beautifully" preserved by the Paton
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,FStuart Paton, former director of J&D
OL,17,FPaton, said: "I am delighted to find a
OL,18,Flong-term home for the collection with
OL,19,FNational Museums Scotland.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]tD@AOUtD@XO]uD@AOUuD@MO]yD@
OL,26,ANOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779069821
OL,3,C'Exceptional' tartan archive gifted to
OL,4,Cthe nation
OL,6,F"The donation is made in memory of my
OL,7,Fgodfather Captain Paton, a long-time
OL,8,Fchairman of the company, in the hopes
OL,9,Fit will become a valuable asset for
OL,10,Fthose researching and learning about
OL,11,FScotland's textile heritage for
OL,12,Fgenerations to come."
OL,14,FNMS is keen to hear from any
OL,15,Fdescendants of employees who worked in
OL,16,FJ&D Paton factories and have any items
OL,17,Frelating to their time there, or have
OL,18,Fmemories or stories that have been
OL,19,Fpassed down through the generations,
OL,20,Fand asked them to get in touch by
OL,21,Fcontacting info@nms.ac.uk
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@UO]
